The paper deals with image search and uses deep convolutional neural networks for supervised learning of hash codes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning models and optimization techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as another possible category. Additionally, the paper involves multimedia and artificial intelligence, which suggests cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as other possible categories.
